{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/25/01/42760189/tesla-says-it-added-11000-superchargers-in-2024", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-02T10:41:25", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-02", "summary": "Tesla opened over 11,000 Supercharger stalls in 2024, bringing the global total to over 65,000. The company added chargers in three new countries during the year. CEO Elon Musk stated that Tesla plans to invest $500 million in network expansion this year, despite previous workforce layoffs in April that impacted 500 members of the charging team.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1011, "out": 129}}
