{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/economics/macro-economic-events/25/01/42850914/us-services-sector-growth-tops-forecasts-but-price-pressures-tariff-concerns-cloud-outlook", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-07T15:38:22", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-07", "summary": "The U.S. Services PMI rose to 54.1% in December 2024, exceeding the 53.3% forecast. Despite growth, the Prices Index jumped to 64.4 from 58.2, driven by input costs and tariff concerns. Markets reacted with rising Treasury yields and a 0.3% climb in the U.S. Dollar Index. Tesla shares fell nearly 4% following a Bank of America downgrade.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1114, "out": 105}}
