{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/analyst-ratings/downgrades/25/01/42923959/evtol-market-soars-too-high-analyst-gives-archer-joby-downgrades", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-10T18:51:20", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-11", "summary": "JPMorgan analyst Bill Peterson downgraded Archer Aviation to Neutral and Joby Aviation to Underweight, citing valuations that have outpaced fundamentals. Peterson noted that market enthusiasm for these stocks has correlated with Tesla and Rocket Lab. He assigned a $9 price target to Archer and a $6 price target to Joby, warning of ongoing certification hurdles and potential capital raises.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1025, "out": 115}}
