{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/analyst-ratings/analyst-color/25/01/43082006/tesla-researcher-says-it-will-help-ev-giants-annual-deliveries-if-trump-does-not-change-ev-tax-credit-eligibility-criteria-immediately", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-20T13:08:15", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-20", "summary": "Researcher Troy Teslike analyzed three potential outcomes for the $7,500 EV tax credit as Donald Trump takes office. Options include restricting eligibility criteria or canceling the credit via Congress. Teslike suggests that leaving criteria untouched while announcing a future cancellation would benefit Tesla's deliveries. Tesla reported 1.79 million global deliveries in 2024, down from 1.81 million in 2023.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1006, "out": 100}}
