{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/25/01/43089109/tesla-senior-exec-pitches-health-reasons-for-adopting-evs-after-president-trump-revoked-bidens-electrification-targets-forget-global-warming", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-21T06:10:19", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-21", "summary": "Following President Trump's revocation of EV targets and potential tax credit repeal, Tesla executive Wes Morrill advocated for EVs based on health benefits like reduced particulate and noise pollution rather than environmental politics. This follows Elon Musk's recent dismissal of near-term climate change concerns and his new role leading the Department of Government Efficiency.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 801, "out": 110}}
