{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/markets/equities/25/01/43122855/trumps-plan-to-revoke-7500-ev-tax-credit-is-a-huge-negative-for-tesla-says-gary-black-downplays-impact-on-rivals", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-22T11:43:41", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-22", "summary": "Gary Black, managing partner of The Future Fund, stated that the potential removal of the $7,500 federal EV tax credit by the Trump administration would be a significant negative for Tesla. Black argued that because the U.S. accounts for 30-35% of Tesla's global volume compared to 4-5% for rivals like GM, Ford, and Stellantis, the impact on Tesla is disproportionately higher. While Elon Musk has suggested the removal would only slightly impact Tesla and hurt competitors, Black remains skeptical, noting that previous price cuts led to industry-wide price wars that harmed Tesla's stock.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 816, "out": 132}}
{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/tech/25/01/43122049/california-law-enforcement-impressed-by-upfitted-tesla-police-vehicle-i-pretty-much-didnt-want-to-be-in-the-explorer-anymore", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-22T11:01:15", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-22", "summary": "California law enforcement officials expressed positive feedback after testing Tesla vehicles upfitted for police use by Unplugged Performance. During a December event, officers compared the Tesla to a Ford Explorer Police Interceptor Utility, with some noting the Tesla was more enjoyable to drive. An upgraded Model Y AWD Patrol vehicle is priced at $92,580, compared to $89,600 for the Ford Police Interceptor Utility AWD Hybrid.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 816, "out": 132}}
{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/tech/25/01/43120972/tesla-looks-to-hire-data-labelers-to-boost-autonomous-vehicle-and-bot-development", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-22T09:02:00", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-22", "summary": "Tesla is hiring full-time data labelers in Utah to process visual data from its vehicle fleet and humanoid bots to advance autonomous software. Employees will work 9 am to 5:30 pm, five days a week, using in-house tools. CEO Elon Musk has previously stated plans to deploy self-driving Model 3 and Model Y vehicles for ride-hailing in 2025, pending regulatory approval, and aims for low-volume production of Optimus robots for factory use in 2025, with potential sales at $10,000 to $20,000 in 2026.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 816, "out": 132}}
{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/tech/25/01/43118289/trump-open-to-elon-musk-or-larry-ellison-buying-tiktok-calls-us-permit-key-to-1-trillion-valuation", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-22T01:33:52", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-22", "summary": "President Donald Trump expressed openness to Tesla CEO Elon Musk or Oracle Chairman Larry Ellison acquiring TikTok. Trump suggested a potential arrangement where half of TikTok's ownership would transfer to the U.S. government in exchange for operating permits, claiming the platform could be worth $1 trillion. This follows an executive order suspending TikTok's ban for 75 days, while the company faces a legal requirement to divest its U.S. operations.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 816, "out": 132}}
{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/trading-ideas/movers/25/01/43177671/micron-technology-shares-are-falling-whats-going-on", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-23T21:27:37", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-24", "summary": "Micron Technology shares fell 4.02% to $104.84 on Thursday, influenced by negative sentiment regarding U.S. export restrictions on AI chips and skepticism from Tesla CEO Elon Musk regarding the $500 billion Stargate AI project. Musk claimed that lead investor SoftBank had secured well under $10 billion in funding for the initiative, which aims to build a network of data centers starting in Abilene, Texas.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 816, "out": 132}}
