{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/trading-ideas/movers/25/01/43289107/will-deepseek-hurt-magnificent-7-stocks-valuation", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-28T21:47:15", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-29", "summary": "A Benzinga reader poll found 57% of respondents believe the emergence of Chinese AI company DeepSeek could pressure the valuations of Magnificent 7 stocks. On Monday, Nvidia shares fell 16.86% and Tesla fell 2.32%, though most stocks rebounded on Tuesday. Tesla, Meta, and Microsoft are scheduled to report earnings after market close Wednesday, while Apple reports Thursday.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1029, "out": 133}}
