{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/25/01/43295689/tesla-gears-up-for-q4-print-here-are-the-recent-forecast-changes-from-wall-streets-most-accurate-analysts", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-29T08:20:53", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-29", "summary": "Tesla will report Q4 2024 earnings on January 29, 2025, with analysts expecting $0.74 EPS and $27.13 billion in revenue. Recent analyst actions include: Wedbush (Daniel Ives) maintained Outperform, raised target to $550; Piper Sandler (Alexander Potter) maintained Overweight, raised target to $500; Morgan Stanley (Adam Jonas) maintained Overweight, raised target to $430; Truist (William Stein) maintained Hold, cut target to $351; and Mizuho (Vijay Rakesh) upgraded to Outperform, raised target to $515.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1109, "out": 114}}
