{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/tech/25/01/43378534/tesla-marks-white-interiors-on-launch-series-of-refreshed-model-y-as-sold-out-before-deliveries-begin", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-31T09:24:59", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-31", "summary": "Tesla has marked the white interior option as sold out for the launch series of the refreshed Model Y in the U.S. before deliveries begin in March. The launch series is priced at $59,990. CEO Elon Musk noted that factories will begin producing the new Model Y in February, warning that retooling and ramp-related costs will impact margins.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 907, "out": 106}}
