{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/markets/equities/25/01/43373930/ross-gerber-says-robotaxi-is-here-and-it-is-a-waymo-from-google-highlights-teslas-severe-hardware-limitations", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-01-31T01:44:04", "effective_trading_date": "2025-01-31", "summary": "Investor Ross Gerber criticized Tesla's Full Self-Driving (FSD) system, citing 'severe hardware limitations' and praising competitor Waymo's autonomous technology. Gerber noted that Tesla's vision-only approach struggles with environmental factors like dust, ash, and sun glare. Tesla is currently under an NHTSA investigation regarding 2.6 million FSD-equipped vehicles, while CEO Elon Musk maintains that FSD will exceed human driving safety by Q2 2025.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 891, "out": 110}}
