{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/analyst-ratings/analyst-color/25/02/43431558/elon-musks-tesla-to-shift-model-y-exports-to-canada-via-berlin-as-trudeau-trump-amp-up-the-trade-war-with-tariffs-and-counter-tariffs-says-researcher", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-03T12:53:59", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-03", "summary": "Researcher Troy Teslike expects Tesla to import Model Y vehicles into Canada from its Berlin gigafactory due to new 25% retaliatory tariffs on U.S. imports effective February 4, 2025. Tesla previously stopped importing from China after Canada increased tariffs on Chinese EVs to 100% on October 1, 2024. Tesla sold 48,000 cars in Canada in 2024.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1160, "out": 96}}
