{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/25/02/43429276/former-tesla-exec-slams-trump-tariffs-lumping-mexicocanada-with-china-is-just-stupid", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-03T11:13:38", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-03", "summary": "Former Tesla executive Rohan Patel criticized President Trump's 25% tariffs on Mexico and Canada and 10% on China as a 'trade bomb' that creates global distrust. Automakers including Tesla and GM are expected to be impacted. Tesla previously postponed plans for a Mexican gigafactory due to tariff concerns. S&P Global Mobility noted a 25% duty could add $6,250 to the cost of vehicles from Mexico and Canada.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1160, "out": 96}}
