{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/25/02/43456592/tesla-researcher-expects-cybertruck-deliveries-to-fall-in-2025-order-backlog-is-gone", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-04T10:40:25", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-04", "summary": "Researcher Troy Teslike predicts Tesla will sell 21,000 Cybertrucks in 2025, significantly below the 65,000 units estimated by Wall Street analysts. Teslike noted 34,426 deliveries in 2024 and claimed the order backlog is exhausted, with 10,600 unsold units at year-end. He dismissed the likelihood of a cheaper variant this year, citing lack of profitability.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1076, "out": 121}}
