{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/25/02/43534797/tesla-sales-drop-60-in-germany-are-elon-musks-politics-getting-in-the-way-of-ev-growth", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-06T16:08:36", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-07", "summary": "Tesla experienced significant sales declines in several European markets in January, including a 59.5% drop in Germany, 63.4% in France, and 75.4% in Spain. The overall drop for these combined markets was 50.4% year-over-year. Analysts suggest these declines may be linked to the Model Y refresh and CEO Elon Musk's political activities, including his support for the Alternative for Germany party. Tesla's brand value reportedly declined by $15 billion in 2024.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 816, "out": 120}}
