{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/tech/25/02/43520687/byd-overtakes-tesla-in-uk-after-elon-musk-led-ev-makers-new-vehicle-registrations-drop-in-january", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-06T08:46:51", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-06", "summary": "BYD overtook Tesla in UK new vehicle registrations in January, with 1,614 registrations compared to Tesla's 1,458. Tesla's UK registrations fell from 1,581 in January 2024. Globally, BYD reclaimed the title of the world's largest battery electric vehicle (BEV) seller in the fourth quarter of 2024, delivering 595,413 BEVs compared to Tesla's 495,570.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 816, "out": 120}}
