{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/25/02/43552235/tesla-hikes-model-x-price-by-5000-making-it-more-expensive-than-cybertruck", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-07T06:02:22", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-07", "summary": "Tesla increased the price of the Model X by $5,000, with the all-wheel drive version now priced at $84,990 and the Plaid variant at $99,990. This price hike makes the base Model X ineligible for the $7,500 federal EV tax credit, which requires a price below $80,000.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 841, "out": 96}}
