{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/25/02/43591152/tariffs-trade-wars-teslas-dilemma-is-the-ev-boom-hitting-a-roadblock", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-10T13:23:35", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-10", "summary": "Potential tariffs on Canadian and Mexican auto imports could increase car prices by $3,000, while proposed tariffs on Chinese graphite, a critical battery component, could rise up to 920%. JPMorgan warns these costs, combined with potential loss of the $7,500 EV tax credit, may slow U.S. EV adoption and squeeze margins for companies like Tesla.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1031, "out": 97}}
{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/tech/25/02/43590034/tesla-researcher-ponders-on-need-for-rain-sensors-after-cybertruck-on-fsd-crashes-with-pole-says-it-doesnt-seem-ready-for-driverless-operation-yet", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-10T12:49:50", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-10", "summary": "Tesla researcher Troy Teslike questioned the readiness of Tesla's Full Self-Driving (FSD) technology after a Cybertruck crashed into a light pole in Nevada. Teslike noted the lack of a dedicated rain sensor and difficulties with object detection in poor visibility. The NHTSA is currently investigating 2.4 million Tesla vehicles regarding FSD performance in reduced visibility conditions.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1031, "out": 97}}
{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/25/02/43589901/the-potential-merger-of-chinese-carmakers-dongfeng-and-changan-likely-to-cast-a-shadow-on-tesla-rival-byd", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-10T12:46:55", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-10", "summary": "State-owned Chinese automakers Dongfeng Motor Group and Chongqing Changan Automobile are considering a merger that could surpass BYD in market dominance. In 2024, their combined sales reached 5.16 million vehicles compared to BYD's 4.27 million. Meanwhile, BYD reported a 551% surge in UK EV registrations for January, while Tesla saw a 7.79% decline.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1031, "out": 97}}
