{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/25/02/43724986/uber-ceo-looks-forward-to-tesla-partnership-for-robotaxis-no-one-wants-to-compete-against-tesla-or-elon", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-14T11:34:29", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-14", "summary": "Uber CEO Dara Khosrowshahi expressed interest in a partnership to deploy Tesla's autonomous vehicles on the Uber platform, stating he prefers not to compete with Tesla. Uber previously exited the self-driving car business in 2020. Tesla CEO Elon Musk plans to begin robotaxi ride-hailing operations in Austin in June, envisioning a fleet model where both Tesla and individual owners contribute vehicles.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1101, "out": 120}}
