{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/25/02/43718656/will-tesla-finally-enter-india-modi-musk-meeting-reportedly-focused-on-tariffs-starlink-licensing-and-spacex-collaboration", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-14T01:50:59", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-14", "summary": "Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi met with Tesla and SpaceX CEO Elon Musk in Washington, D.C. Discussions reportedly covered Tesla's potential entry into India, Starlink's licensing application, and potential SpaceX-ISRO collaborations. Musk has advocated for reduced tariffs on Tesla vehicles to export low-cost models to India. Tesla's stock closed at $355.94, up 5.77%, and climbed 0.53% in after-hours trading to $357.81.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 845, "out": 97}}
{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/markets/equities/25/02/43755111/billionaire-investor-dan-loeb-boosts-stake-in-mark-zuckerbergs-meta-elon-musks-tesla-but-sold-these-three-mag-7-stocks-in-q4", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-15T08:41:43", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-15", "summary": "Activist investor Dan Loeb's Third Point LLC increased its stake in Tesla by 25% (100,000 shares) during the fourth quarter of 2024. The fund also increased holdings in Meta Platforms and Flutter Entertainment, while trimming positions in Microsoft and Amazon and selling its entire Apple stake.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 845, "out": 97}}
