{"article_id": "https://www.benzinga.com/general/space/25/02/43802341/elon-musk-says-spacex-created-history-by-blasting-off-a-rocket-from-one-country-and-landing-it-another-this-is-the-first-time", "symbol": "TSLA", "source_datetime_utc": "2025-02-19T01:29:13", "effective_trading_date": "2025-02-19", "summary": "SpaceX successfully landed a Falcon 9 rocket booster off The Bahamas, marking its first international landing. CEO Elon Musk also reiterated plans to launch Tesla's Optimus humanoid robots to Mars on Starship rockets in 2026. SpaceX currently manages approximately $20 billion in government contracts.", "model": "gemini-3.1-flash-lite", "tokens": {"in": 1018, "out": 88}}
